Dollycam application
====================

For compilation is neccesary to have installed following libraries. See libralies_list file for details.

 * boost - threading
 * gSoap - communication with the application
 * gphoto2 - communication with a camera
 * libxml2 - XML processing 

At firs, check the definition of serial port for communication with motor control board in serial.c file. To compile, change path to dollycam source directory and make build directory for cmake files.

$ cd dollycam
$ mkdir build
$ cd build
$ cmake ..
$ make

Binary is located in dollycam/build/bin directory. 

MJPG streamer
=============

Libjpeg must be installed before compilation. Easy to compile:

$ cd mjpg-streamer
$ make






